{"tid":1354374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯：為何要與白衣人割蓆？","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T07:00:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"33b7421bd56b7727cf5dd63d29d353a9fc8e9aa5","tid":1354374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1469935_2_20190723142157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1469935_2_20190723142157.jpg&h=6e17536f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民計劃周末發起光復元朗行動，立法會議員何君堯呼籲，所有市民無論身穿甚麼顏色衣服，都不應訴諸暴力，強調任何人士犯法都要受到法律制裁。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯出席本台節目「視點31」錄影後接受記者訪問，被問到會否與「白衣人」割蓆，他反問為何要與穿白衣的人割蓆，重申任何人犯法，都不應姑息。<br />\n<br />\n至於會否向元朗鄉民呼籲，周末不要與發起光復行動的市民發生衝突，何君堯說，不介意呼籲，強調如果香港要尋求出路，應全部暫停所有遊行及和平示威，香港便有時間喘息。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯說，他在新界並非很有影響力，但都會呼籲所有人，包括新界村民要冷靜，又建議民主派不要煽動市民訴諸暴力。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯離開港台電視大廈時，一班市民在門口守候，有人向他掟鞋及指罵，何君堯呼籲冷靜，又邀請大家下月4日出席集會傾談。<br />\n<br />\n有市民質問他，有無申請美國國籍，他否認，又說很多網上傳言都是假，重申沒有外國居留權，至於會否譴責當日元朗站打人的「白衣人」，何君堯說，會一視同仁譴責，包括在西環衝擊的暴徒。"},{"pid":"e57d776e99a44b52f83c4a01706e4180a32f772c","tid":1354374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469935-20190723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469935-20190723.htm&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=d8ceb7d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1469935-20190723.htm&h=a7c9e433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1469935-20190723.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8245fae30d799da7484486b046406dd87ed9fb0e","tid":1354374,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFqibUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFqibUD.jpg&h=ebc0d1d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRtS0NX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRtS0NX.jpg&h=7578d7a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n十八鄉連儂牆準備上線啦!"},{"pid":"52dffa095041117813791a167f7e7fa9154967fd","tid":1354374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b4ef7412fea3af1302686348abf6c5523d2de1","tid":1354374,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:33:39.000Z","msg":"「沒有外國居留權」，係申請緊？"},{"pid":"8c36314df0137a0ca35d2140c983a22e0e11ca9f","tid":1354374,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6c18c04831336789f7d17dbb1df1f1622afb07","tid":1354374,"uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:00:06.000Z","msg":"即係有你份"}]}